rows.label: qst650401_msg0001
rows.name: Hey, that's Levchina...

rows.label: qst650401_msg0002
rows.name:
I wonder what's wrong.
We should go talk to her.

rows.label: qst650401_msg0003
rows.name: Has something happened?

rows.label: qst650401_msg0004
rows.name:
It's the children... The three of them
went out to play at the edge of the
village, but haven't come back yet...

rows.label: qst650401_msg0005
rows.name:
Is that Nascion, Arin, and Arina
you're talking about?

rows.label: qst650401_msg0006
rows.name: That's right, Rex.

rows.label: qst650401_msg0007
rows.name: Are those the kids we spoke to before?

rows.label: qst650401_msg0008
rows.name: Yeah, that's right.

rows.label: qst650401_msg0009
rows.name:
That's a little worrying, huh...
We'll have to find them, quick!

rows.label: qst650401_msg0010
rows.name: Come on everyone, let's get a move on!

rows.label: qst650401_msg0011
rows.name: Rex, hey, hold up a minute.

rows.label: qst650401_msg0012
rows.name: What's up?

rows.label: qst650401_msg0013
rows.name:
I, um... It's my husband, too...
He went to look for the kids and
never came back, either...

rows.label: qst650401_msg0014
rows.name: Raymon, too?!

rows.label: qst650401_msg0015
rows.name: This very bad news...

rows.label: qst650401_msg0016
rows.name: We really do have to find them quick.

rows.label: qst650401_msg0017
rows.name:
Levchina-san, any idea where could
Raymon and littlepon go?

rows.label: qst650401_msg0018
rows.name:
The kids said they were going to play
in the direction of Ysheva Harbor, so
you might have a look there...

rows.label: qst650401_msg0019
rows.name: Got it. It's just the next island over.

rows.label: qst650401_msg0020
rows.name: No time to waste then, Rex.

rows.label: qst650401_msg0021
rows.name: Agreed!
